data.description: Be the first to enjoy a brand new build from Taylor Morrison Homes with this pristine three bedroom, two and a half bath townhome. Upon entering into the main floor, you're greeted with a sunny and open floor plan. The kitchen has a large island, all new stainless steel appliances and a large pantry. The adjacent family room looks out onto the patio and enjoys a view of the large pond. The washer and dryer are strategically located on the second floor, close to the bedrooms and an additional bathroom. The primary bedroom has an en-suite bathroom with dual sinks and a tiled shower with sliding doors. The second and third bedrooms are well proportioned and bright, with lots of natural light.  Your amenities included with ownership; a large community pool, tennis and racketball courts, and a large playground. Conveniently located near I75 and Highway 681, 5 miles from the new Sarasota Memorial Hospital in Venice,  about 7 minutes to Nokomis Beach and amid countless shops for groceries, restaurants and more!  Sarasota County is the home of top rated schools and beaches awaiting you!
